abstract: >-
  A zero-shot geometric anomaly detector for LLM residual streams.
  The method identifies harmful or anomalous prompts by measuring
  angular deviations from a normative (safe) manifold in hidden
  representations, using PCA-derived reference directions and
  Gaussian Mixture Model scoring. No harmful examples are required
  at fit time under the normative reference strategy.
